{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_019D3YXSdqSE6ejdkcRnPsem","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now fix the health endpoint issue. The problem is that Quarkus serves health at `/q/health` by default and `quarkus.smallrye-health.root-path=/health` controls the path under the management interface root (default `/q/`). To get `/health` directly, I need to set the management root path or change the approach. Let me fix the config and also add startup check disabling:"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1301,"cache_read_input_tokens":67192,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":1301,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":551},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c8c0436c-69f4-4378-aa8f-dd3eb0ddb087","uuid":"767ced42-b7c3-4908-ad21-b9218c38468f"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_019D3YXSdqSE6ejdkcRnPsem","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01PxXnur3KL34V1WBHX617xL","name":"Edit","input":{"file_path":"/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__coffee-shop__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/orders-service/src/main/resources/application.properties","old_string":"# Health check\nquarkus.smallrye-health.root-path=/health\n\n# Disable Kafka health/startup checks\nquarkus.kafka.health.enabled=false\nquarkus.messaging.kafka.health.enabled=false\nmp.messaging.incoming.order-updates.health-readiness-enabled=false\nmp.messaging.outgoing.barista.health-readiness-enabled=false\nmp.messaging.outgoing.kitchen.health-readiness-enabled=false","new_string":"# Health check — serve at /q/health (Quarkus default)\n# Also expose the non-management path /health via the management interface root\nquarkus.management.enabled=false\nquarkus.smallrye-health.root-path=/health\n\n# Disable Kafka health/startup/readiness checks so app starts without Kafka\nquarkus.kafka.health.enabled=false\nmp.messaging.incoming.order-updates.health-readiness-enabled=false\nmp.messaging.incoming.order-updates.health-startup-enabled=false\nmp.messaging.outgoing.barista.health-readiness-enabled=false\nmp.messaging.outgoing.barista.health-startup-enabled=false\nmp.messaging.outgoing.kitchen.health-readiness-enabled=false\nmp.messaging.outgoing.kitchen.health-startup-enabled=false"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1301,"cache_read_input_tokens":67192,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":1301,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":551},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c8c0436c-69f4-4378-aa8f-dd3eb0ddb087","uuid":"eea1d020-33d8-457e-8d66-e207414f4682"}
