{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01HwjTg2rj15xwJvubHFoXbx","type":"tool_result","content":"2026-03-14 10:05:22,666 ERROR [io.qua.ver.htt.run.QuarkusErrorHandler] (executor-thread-1) HTTP Request to /api/orders failed, error id: bdc35c65-807b-4ca6-b65a-1576b2b33ea6-1: jakarta.validation.UnexpectedTypeException: HV000030: No validator could be found for constraint 'jakarta.validation.constraints.Min' validating type 'java.lang.Integer'. Check configuration for 'place.arg0.quantity'\n\tat org.hibernate.validator.internal.engine.constraintvalidation.ConstraintTree.getExceptionForNullValidator(ConstraintTree.java:116)","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c8c0436c-69f4-4378-aa8f-dd3eb0ddb087","uuid":"68b84144-cbfe-427f-b4d0-876835ac8aa9"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01Kmd3sPkHY4QFruM1DEZrrJ","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The validation error changed - now it's `@Min` on `int` type but it says `java.lang.Integer`. The issue is that Quarkus is validating the method parameters of `OrderService.place(@Valid OrderRequest req)` and it's looking at the parameter types at the method level.\n\nWait, the error says `place.arg0.quantity` - this is cascaded validation from the `@Valid` annotation on the method parameter. The `@Min` constraint is being applied to `quantity` but the validator can't find a proper validator for `Integer` with `@Min`. Actually, `@Min` should work fine with `int`/`Integer`. \n\nThe issue might be that Bean Validation is cascading through the method parameter and treating the object's fields differently. Let me try a different approach - instead of `@Valid` on the service, add it directly to the resource parameter:"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":372,"cache_read_input_tokens":77193,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":372,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":324},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c8c0436c-69f4-4378-aa8f-dd3eb0ddb087","uuid":"31de2868-91ce-45cd-84f2-1a2c1ffee9be"}
