{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01R2bQYmU24o5p3w2tCtFPMF","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All tasks are complete. Here's a summary of the migration:\n\n## Migration Complete: Jakarta EE (Open Liberty) to Quarkus 3.17.8\n\n### Key Changes Made\n1. **Build system**: Replaced Liberty Maven plugin and Jakarta EE/MicroProfile BOMs with Quarkus BOM and `quarkus-maven-plugin`\n2. **JSON serialization**: Jakarta JSON-B/JSON-P replaced with Jackson `ObjectMapper`\n3. **JPA**: `@PersistenceContext` replaced with `@Inject EntityManager`\n4. **Bean Validation**: Converted `OrderRequest` from record to POJO; replaced `@NotBlank` with `@NotNull @Size(min=1)` for Quarkus build-time compatibility; added `quarkus.index-dependency` for the common module\n5. **Configuration**: Liberty `server.xml` + `persistence.xml` replaced with `application.properties`; H2 in-memory as default datasource; PostgreSQL available via `%pg` profile\n6. **Kafka**: SmallRye Kafka connector with `lazy-client=true` for graceful startup without broker\n7. **Static resources**: Moved from `src/main/webapp/` to `src/main/resources/META-INF/resources/`\n8. **Dockerfiles**: Updated to build Quarkus uber-jars and run with `java -jar`\n\n### Smoke Test Results\n**11/11 checks passed** (0 failures):\n- Health check: 200 UP\n- Create beverage order: 202 Accepted\n- Get order by ID: 200 with correct data and PLACED status\n- Create food order: 202 Accepted\n- Validation: 400 Bad Request for missing fields\n- Static content: 200 OK"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":576,"cache_read_input_tokens":100148,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":576,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":421},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c8c0436c-69f4-4378-aa8f-dd3eb0ddb087","uuid":"5ee7f03f-f062-4a0d-868b-f8bb9130b6b1"}
